file.name: SimpleCallbackWithOperationResource.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /simplecallback:
    get:
      summary: Simple get operation
      operationId: getWithNoParameters
      responses:
        "200":
          description: voila!
      callbacks:
        testCallback1:
          http://www.url.com:
            get:
              summary: get all the reviews
              operationId: getAllReviews
              responses:
                "200":
                  description: successful operation
                  content:
                    application/json:
                      schema:
                        type: integer
                        format: int32
